    "\", p.924 17 Kaal [105] Deposits & loans \"Parties in the supply chain can view inventory records and effect payments in real-time and could facilitate a seamless system of lending and repayment using smart contracts.",
    "\", p.924 17 Kaal [105] Wealth & asset management \"For example, several DeFi protocols enable decentralized peer-to-peer token exchanges (DEXs)\", p.925 17 Kaal [105] Deposits & loans \"Lending and borrowing of digital assets is one of the most common services DeFi protocols make available to their users.",
    "\", p.926 17 Kaal [105] Payments \"The remittance market is similar to the loan market with regards to the potential for disruption by DeFi Dapps.",
    "\", p.927 17 Kaal [105] Exchanges derivatives Wealth & asset management Data \"The trading of digital assets is another significant market segment of DeFi Dapps.",
    "Several DeFi protocols enable derivatives, margin trading, and prediction markets on Ethereum."
